replyContent: Thank you! Feedback like yours keeps us going. And feedback like yours keeps us looking for things we can improve, too. If you can think of something that'd make learning to code on Mimo better, please tell us at feedback@getmimo.com. High fives!

Very buggy interface. Characters that disappear or get overwritten, cursor often jumps back to the start of the line. replyContent: Hi Abdullah. Many thanks for submitting your review, your feedback is much appreciated. We are glad to hear that you like our app and that you find it really useful and easy to use. Yes, only the first two lessons of each course is for free, as this is how much free content we can afford while paying rent and salaries. Have a nice day! Cheers!
